      "description": "Budget-friendly and ready for its next chapter, this vehicle offers practical transportation at an accessible price point. It shows its age and is best suited for a value-minded buyer looking for dependable basic use, a starter vehicle, or a project with potential. An honest opportunity to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget.",
