      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a budget-friendly car with plenty of potential for the right buyer. It\u2019s not pretending to be perfect, but it\u2019s an honest, affordable option for someone who needs inexpensive wheels, a project, or a parts car with value left in it. If you\u2019re handy or just looking for a cheap way to get into something without spending big, this could be a great fit. Priced to move and worth a look.",
