    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Solid budget-friendly project with a tough, no-nonsense mechanical feel and plenty of usable life for the right owner. It shows cosmetic wear and age, but the drivetrain pulls through, the chassis feels honest, and it remains a practical, affordable way into dependable transportation. A good candidate for someone who knows their way around basic maintenance and wants a capable car without spending big money. Priced to move, with enough upside left for a handy buyer.",
